author: MATTHEW DALY / AP
title: Sen. Rand Paul Remained at Work on U.S. Capitol For Six Days After Coronavirus Test
description: Sen. Rand Paul's coronavirus diagnosis has led Utah’s two GOP senators — Mike Lee and Mitt Romney — to place themselves into quarantine
